channel.title: Edited my server and commands got raped
channel.description: I modified my server by adding a few new commands such as Holy Force, making pickup admin only, and speeding up my computer by modifying the way it dealt with packets. It didn't go so well. I logged in on the main guy, and the main screen was black, but I could click on different tabs (Quest, skill, prayer, etc.) I deleted everything that had to do with RS2 Private servers, re-installed Tru3scape and the commands didn't work. Please I need help with this. The Client is SIlabsoft v7 webclient and the server is Tru3scape.
